  "title": "Maximum lock angle (steering angle)",
  "htmlContent": "<div class=\"content\">\n\r\n<table width=\"100%\" >\r\n  <!--XPRINT-->\r\n  <table>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td></td>\r\n   <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n  \t\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  \r\n  <!--/XPRINT-->\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td >\n<p class=\"title\">Maximum lock angle (steering angle)</p>\n\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95%\">\n<p>The maximum angle of lock (3) is the angle which the wheels\nadopt at the full steering angle (left and right) relative to the\naxis of symmetry (2). This determines the vehicle's turning\ncircle.</p>\n\n<p>The maximum angle of lock behaves like the toe variation angle\nand also provides information on the status of the steering trapeze\nand steering mechanism.</p>\n\n<p>As the adjustment of maximum angle of lock is usually only\npossible with off-road vehicles, this should only be checked in\nthis type of vehicle.</p>\n\n<p>The maximum angle of lock is measured with the relevant internal\ncornering wheel fully locked (3). Depending upon the steering\ntrapezium, the external cornering wheel (1) must have the same\nnegative difference, within a specified tolerance.</p>\n\n<p class=\"bold\">Example</p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" class=\"border-none\">\n<colgroup>\n<col width=\"72%\" align=\"left\">\n<col width=\"28%\" align=\"left\"></colgroup>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Maximum angle of lock, right (2):</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>34&deg;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Angle of lock, left (3)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>32&deg; &plusmn; 1&deg;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Difference (1):</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>2&deg;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>Tolerance:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p>&plusmn; 1&deg;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n </td>\n<td valign=\"top\" align=\"right\"><!--SCDS Link: H2027.itf-->\n<img border=\"0\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" alt=\n\"Object Number: 2400758  Size: DEFAULT\" align=\"TOP\" src=\"/data/assets/images/2649f3f9616e.jpg\">\n<br>\n<a href=\"javascript:TFormSubmit('A23J1PGI1AFI1','1','A23J1PGI1AFI1','detail')\">\n<img src=\"/data/assets/images/db1138827f57.gif\" alt=\n\"Click here for detailed picture of above image\"></a>\n\n<br> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" class=\"border-all\">\n<colgroup>\n<col align=\"left\"></colgroup>\n\n<tr valign=\"bottom\">\n<th class=\"border-bot\" rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"bold\">Effects of incorrect measurement angles</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td class=\"border-none\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n<li>different turning circle of the vehicle</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  \r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td ></td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>",
